<%= render :partial => "content", locals: { page: 2 } %>

<h1 class="part-title">Set up access in Digital Prison Services</h1>
<div class="govuk-inset-text">
  Local System Administrator (LSA) task
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-column">
  <div class="govuk-body">

    <p>
      All HOMDs/HoOMUs, OMU case admin staff and POMs need to have the right roles assigned to them in order to access the allocations service.
    </p>

    <p>Sign in to Digital Prison Services using your Desktop Icon and LSA Credentials:
      <%= image_tag("help_step2/dps_desktop_icon.png", width: 79, height: 95, style: "vertical-align: middle", alt: "Desktop icon for Digital Prison Services") %>
    </p>

    <p><%=image_tag("help_step2/hmpps_login_image.png") %></p>

    <ul class="govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>
        <div>Select ‘Manage User Accounts’</div><br>
        <div><%=image_tag("help_step2/dps_select_service.png", width: 999, height: 430) %></div><br>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div>Select ‘Search for DPS User’</div><br>
        <div><%=image_tag("help_step2/manage_user_accounts.png", width: 392, height: 288) %></div><br>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div>Search for the staff member you want to set up by entering their user ID</div><br>
        <div><%=image_tag("help_step2/search_dps_user.png", width: 840, height: 411) %></div><br>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div>When you have found the staff member, click on their Name</div><br>
        <div><%=image_tag("help_step2/user_search_results.png", width: 1226, height: 352) %></div><br>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div>Click ‘Add Another Role’</div><br>
        <div><%=image_tag("help_step2/user_roles.png", width: 552, height: 396) %></div><br>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div>Select the Allocations – POM role for POMs. HOMDs and case admins need the Allocations – HOMD role. Choose confirm.
        </div><br>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <%= render :partial => "next_link", locals: { url: help_step3_path, next_page_title: 'Set up POMs in NOMIS'} %>
  </div>
</div>
